  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thou, who dost summon great heroes, art here to answer the call of the Marquis of the Kingdom. The Marquis hath lost all contact with the palace, and no investigators returned. Thou art commanded to investigate what transpired within the palace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/390731f88847c999f839adbe98b277af.avif?t=1746594360\" width=576 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a 'summoner' who summons warriors and heroes to battle. You can choose warriors to battle upon the field using 'mana.' Also, if you level up, you may choose to summon a powerful hero or upgrade an existing hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/e540b4c6980c1d1361ff5cad42a46780.avif?t=1746594360\" width=724 height=370 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/407e7b9c2087f3f6a8f916ff6ae1ee22.avif?t=1746594360\" width=576 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the village starts providing a defensive tower or supporting attacks, you can upgrade your 'mana.'</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Summon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/e118f44c1f442338969553eeeb066c6e.avif?t=1746594360\" width=576 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need 'mana' to summon a warrior. Please summon carefully.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Win</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/71e17b4a7d95e7ab8f0c1181df70a0f3.avif?t=1746594360\" width=432 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat the inundating enemies, smash away defense towers, and defeat the boss to win the battle.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thou, who dost summon great heroes, art here to answer the call of the Marquis of the Kingdom. The Marquis hath lost all contact with the palace, and no investigators returned. Thou art commanded to investigate what transpired within the palace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/390731f88847c999f839adbe98b277af.avif?t=1746594360\" width=576 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a 'summoner' who summons warriors and heroes to battle. You can choose warriors to battle upon the field using 'mana.' Also, if you level up, you may choose to summon a powerful hero or upgrade an existing hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/e540b4c6980c1d1361ff5cad42a46780.avif?t=1746594360\" width=724 height=370 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/407e7b9c2087f3f6a8f916ff6ae1ee22.avif?t=1746594360\" width=576 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the village starts providing a defensive tower or supporting attacks, you can upgrade your 'mana.'</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Summon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/e118f44c1f442338969553eeeb066c6e.avif?t=1746594360\" width=576 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need 'mana' to summon a warrior. Please summon carefully.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Win</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564360/extras/71e17b4a7d95e7ab8f0c1181df70a0f3.avif?t=1746594360\" width=432 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat the inundating enemies, smash away defense towers, and defeat the boss to win the battle.</p>",
